*Srećno* ga čekam u parku. (I am waiting for him happily in the park.)

Došla sam na kraju *srećno*. (I arrived at the end happily.)

*Srećno* ga srela sam u gradu. (I met him happily in the city.)

Kraj je došao *srećno*. (The end came happily.)

*Srećno* smo se rastali. (We parted happily.)

Radost je bila *srećno* prožeta. (The joy was happily pervaded.)